Based on the EZ-FLASH Omega Definitive Edition kernel by EZ-FLASH
(https://github.com/ez-flash/omega-de-kernel), licensed under Apache-2.0.

Portions of the save-backup feature are ported from the SimpleLight DE fork
by Veikkos and contributors (https://github.com/Sterophonick/omega-de-kernel).

This kernel embeds the Game Boy / Game Boy Color emulator Jagoomba Color
(v0.5, Omega DE build) by EvilJagaGenius
(https://github.com/EvilJagaGenius/jagoombacolor), itself based on Goomba
Color and Goomba by FluBBa. The emulator is a separate work, distributed
under its own terms, and is not covered by the Apache-2.0 license below.

